'''朱迪角龙属'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Judiceratops''}}，发音{{IPAc-en|ˌ|dʒ|uː|d|iː|ˈ|s|ɛr|ə|t|ɒ|p|s}} {{respell|JOO|dee|SERR|ə|tops}}；意为“{{link-en|朱迪斯河组|Judith River Formation}}的有角面孔”）是一属已[[灭绝|灭绝]][[角龙科|角龙科]][[恐龙|恐龙]]，生存于约7800万年前[[白垩纪|晚白垩世]]的美国[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]。像其它角龙科一样，朱迪角龙也是一类大型{{link-en|四足|quadrupedal}}[[食草动物|食草动物]]，并且是已知生存年代最早的[[开角龙亚科|开角龙亚科]]。<ref name=Judiceratops>{{Cite journal | last1 = Longrich | first1 = N. R. | doi = 10.3374/014.054.0103 | title = ''Judiceratops tigris'', a New Horned Dinosaur from the Middle Campanian Judith River Formation of Montana | journal = Bulletin of the Peabody Museum of Natural History | volume = 54 | pages = 51–65 | year = 2013 | pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>

==叙述==
